### Place Coffee Order (Async)
POST http://127.0.0.1:3000/order
Content-Type: application/json
X-Amz-Invocation-Type: Event

{
  "orderId": "test-order-123",
  "attendeeId": "test-attendee-456",
  "eventId": "test-event-789",
  "orderDetails": {
    "drinkType": "latte",
    "size": "medium",
    "customizations": ["extra shot", "oat milk"]
  },
  "timestamp": "2025-11-18T14:00:00Z"
}

### Place Another Coffee Order (Async)
POST http://127.0.0.1:3000/order
Content-Type: application/json
X-Amz-Invocation-Type: Event

{
  "orderId": "test-order-456",
  "attendeeId": "test-attendee-789",
  "eventId": "test-event-789",
  "orderDetails": {
    "drinkType": "cappuccino",
    "size": "large",
    "customizations": ["almond milk"]
  },
  "timestamp": "2025-11-18T15:00:00Z"
}

### Get Execution History
GET http://127.0.0.1:3000/execution/history?executionArn=arn:aws:lambda:us-east-1:123456789012:function:coffee-orders:execution:test-order-123
